author: mbrohl
msg: Applied fix from trunk for revision: 1703954
Applied patch for OFBIZ-6621: MapContext.entrySet() slows down when ByteBuffer objects are in the context.
Introduces a private inner class ListSet representing a Set backed by a List instead of the HashSet implementation.
Thanks Gareth Carter for spotting this and providing the patch.
